Title: Object: The Fifth Plague of Egypt
Series: Liber Studiorum
Description: In the distance, the pyramids are visible, with flames running across the ground in front of them; in the foreground are a low building, broken tree-stumps, a dead horse and rider and two supplicating figures. 10 June 1808 Mezzotint and etching
